snippet: Lethal levels of carbon monoxide filled a music rehearsal studio in Passaic on Saturday, the authorities said.
abstract: Lethal levels of carbon monoxide fill music rehearsal studio in Passaic, NJ, killing two people and sickening dozen more.
lead_paragraph: Lethal levels of carbon monoxide filled a music rehearsal studio in Passaic on Saturday, the authorities said.

headline.main: Carbon Monoxide Kills 2 and Sickens 12 in New Jersey
